{"type":"champion","format":"standAloneComplex","version":"4.12.2","data":{"Khazix":{"id":"Khazix","key":"121","name":"卡力斯","title":"虛空掠食者","image":{"full":"Khazix.png","sprite":"champion1.png","group":"champion","x":96,"y":48,"w":48,"h":48},"skins":[{"id":"121000","num":0,"name":"default"},{"id":"121001","num":1,"name":"機甲騎士 卡力斯"}],"lore":"卡力斯，一位兇惡虛空掠食者，悄悄的侵入瓦羅然，尋找這片大地上最富有生命能量的生物。每當他擊殺一位犧牲者並吞噬他的力量後，卡力斯將會進化的更加強壯。<br><br>當卡力斯剛進入這個世界時，他是非常脆弱且饑餓的。然而，他初次遇到的那些弱小生物，並不足以滿足他對進化的欲望。卡力斯為了達到目的，以自己的生命為代價去挑戰、尋找極度危險的生物。每次的擊殺與蛻變，都讓他成為更加強壯、敏捷的掠食者。卡力斯開始進行肆無忌憚的攻擊行動，相信他目前所擁有的力量是無人可敵的。直到某一天，正當他尋覓著美味的餐點時，他突然從一位掠食者變成了獵物。一道陰影自視野外撲出，以迅速的身影和鋼鐵般的利爪將他壓倒在地上。眼前的咆嘯與毫不留情的爪擊，第一次讓卡力斯見到了自己的血。由內而外的憤怒在此時爆發，銳利的刃劃向這名猛獸的眼，迫使他退後。他們從日出對戰到日落，直至死亡的氣息逼近，他們才不情願地各自離開。當他的傷癒合後，卡力斯萌生了一個想法，他要尋找能跟虛空之力相抗衡的對手並吞噬他。這股新生的動力驅使他開始了新的狩獵行動。總有一天，卡力斯會盡情的虐殺雷葛爾。<br><br>「進化，就是無盡的殺戮與吞噬。」<br>-- 卡力斯","blurb":"卡力斯，一位兇惡虛空掠食者，悄悄的侵入瓦羅然，尋找這片大地上最富有生命能量的生物。每當他擊殺一位犧牲者並吞噬他的力量後，卡力斯將會進化的更加強壯。<br><br>當卡力斯剛進入這個世界時，他是非常脆弱且饑餓的。然而，他初次遇到的那些弱小生物，並不足以滿足他對進化的欲望。卡力斯為了達到目的，以自己的生命為代價去挑戰、尋找極度危險的生物。每次的擊殺與蛻變，都讓他成為更加強壯、敏捷的掠食者。卡力斯開始進行肆無忌憚的攻擊行動，相信他目前所擁有的力量是無人可敵的。...","allytips":["- 當敵人因為身旁沒有友軍而被認定是孤立時，孤獨的恐懼對這些目標的傷害會大幅增加。","- 當敵方隊伍看不到卡力斯時，暗影殺機就會啟動。可借由草叢或是虛空突襲再度啟動。別忘了在有暗影殺機效果時向敵人進行普攻。","- 卡力斯可以自由地選擇何時或何地才是他該加入的戰場。為了勝利請謹慎選擇戰鬥時機。"],"enemytips":["- 孤獨的恐懼對被孤立的目標造成額外的傷害。因此在我方單位較多時，如小兵、英雄和塔旁會比較有優勢。","- 掠翅飛躍和虛空突襲有比較長的冷卻時間。卡力斯在這些技能進入冷卻時，是非常虛弱的。"],"tags":["Assassin","Figher"],"partype":"Mana","info":{"attack":9,"defense":4,"magic":3,"difficulty":7},"stats":{"hp":430.0,"hpperlevel":85.0,"mp":260.0,"mpperlevel":40.0,"movespeed":350.0,"armor":19.0,"armorperlevel":3.0,"spellblock":30.0,"spellblockperlevel":1.25,"attackrange":125.0,"hpregen":6.25,"hpregenperlevel":0.75,"mpregen":6.75,"mpregenperlevel":0.5,"crit":0.0,"critperlevel":0.0,"attackdamage":50.0,"attackdamageperlevel":3.1,"attackspeedoffset":-0.065,"attackspeedperlevel":2.7},"spells":[{"id":"KhazixQ","name":"孤獨的恐懼","description":"卡力斯會自動標記那些因為與其友軍有段距離的敵人，將之歸類於被孤立的目標。孤獨的恐懼除了對單一目標造成物理傷害外，對這類被孤立的目標將造成更多傷害。如果是使用<span class=\"color00DD33\">進化裂刃</span>，傷害更會大幅度的增加。卡力斯基礎攻擊和孤獨的恐懼的距離會隨之增加。","tooltip":"<span class=\"colorFF9900\">被動： </span>標記孤立周圍沒有其他友軍的敵人。<br><br><span class=\"colorFF9900\">主動： </span>造成 {{ e1 }} <span class=\"colorFF8C00\">（+{{ a1 }}）</span> 點物理傷害。如果目標被孤立，則傷害增加到 {{ e6 }} <span class=\"colorFF8C00\">（+{{ a2 }}）</span>。<br><br><span class=\"color00DD33\">進化裂刃：</span>如果目標被孤立，傷害增加到 {{ f3 }} <span class=\"colorFF8C00\">（+{{ f2 }}）</span>。提高卡力斯 {{ e5 }}普攻和孤獨恐懼的距離。","leveltip":{"label":["基礎傷害"],"effect":["{{ e1 }} -> {{ e1NL }}"]},"maxrank":5,"cooldown":[3.5,3.5,3.5,3.5,3.5],"cooldownBurn":"3.5","cost":[25,25,25,25,25],"costBurn":"25","effect":[null,[70,95,120,145,170],[30,30,30,30,30],null,[100,100,100,100,100],[50,50,50,50,50],[91,124,156,189,221]],"effectBurn":[null,"70/95/120/145/170","30",null,"100","50","91/124/156/189/221"],"vars":[{"link":"bonusattackdamage","coeff":1.2,"key":"a1"},{"link":"bonusattackdamage","coeff":1.56,"key":"a2"}],"costType":"Mana","range":[325,325,325,325,325],"rangeBurn":"325","image":{"full":"KhazixQ.png","sprite":"spell4.png","group":"spell","x":240,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48},"altimages":[{"full":"KhazixQ0.png","sprite":"spell12.png","group":"spell","x":336,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48}],"resource":"{{ cost }} 魔力"},{"id":"KhazixW","name":"虛空尖刺","description":"卡力斯發射爆裂尖刺，對周圍所有敵人緩速並且造成物理傷害。卡力斯如果在爆炸半徑內，則會獲得治療效果。如果選擇 <span class=\"color00DD33\">進化尖刺拷問</span>，虛空尖刺會在錐形範圍內射擊 3 發尖刺，並且增加其緩速效果。","tooltip":"發射爆裂尖刺，對周圍所有敵人造成 {{ e1 }} <span class=\"colorFF8C00\">（+{{ a1 }}）</span> 點物理傷害（對野怪造成 20% 額外傷害）並緩速他們 {{ e3 }}% ，持續 {{ e4 }} 秒。如果卡力斯在爆炸半徑內，則獲得 {{ e2 }}<span class=\"color99FF99\">（+{{ a2 }}）</span> 治療效果。<br><br><span class=\"color00DD33\">進化尖刺拷問： </span>會在錐形範圍內射擊三發尖刺並且增加 {{ e5 }}% 緩速效果，持續 {{ e4 }} 秒。若被攻擊單位為敵方英雄，則獲得其視野，持續 2 秒。（不影響潛行單位）","leveltip":{"label":["傷害","治療","魔力消耗"],"effect":["{{ e1 }} -> {{ e1NL }}","{{ e2 }} -> {{ e2NL }}","{{ cost }} -> {{ costnNL }}"]},"maxrank":5,"cooldown":[8,8,8,8,8],"cooldownBurn":"8","cost":[55,60,65,70,75],"costBurn":"55/60/65/70/75","effect":[null,[75,115,155,195,235],[40,70,100,130,160],[20,20,20,20,20],[2,2,2,2,2],[50,50,50,50,50]],"effectBurn":[null,"75/115/155/195/235","40/70/100/130/160","20","2","50"],"vars":[{"link":"bonusattackdamage","coeff":1.0,"key":"a1"},{"link":"spelldamage","coeff":0.5,"key":"a2"}],"costType":"Mana","range":[1000,1000,1000,1000,1000],"rangeBurn":"1000","image":{"full":"KhazixW.png","sprite":"spell4.png","group":"spell","x":288,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48},"altimages":[{"full":"KhazixW0.png","sprite":"spell12.png","group":"spell","x":384,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48}],"resource":"{{ cost }} 魔力"},{"id":"KhazixE","name":"掠翅飛躍","description":"卡力斯奮身跳向目標區域，落地時對敵人造成物理傷害。如果施放的是進化技能<span class=\"color00DD33\"> 進化飛翅</span>的話，可以大幅提高飛躍的距離。當擊殺英雄或造成助攻時，還可以立即重置掠翅飛躍的冷卻時間。","tooltip":"跳向指定區域，造成 {{ e1 }} <span class=\"colorFF8C00\">（+{{ a1 }}）</span> 物理傷害。<br><br><span class=\"color00DD33\">進化飛翅：</span>增加掠翅飛躍的距離。擊殺敵方英雄或是助攻將會刷新掠翅飛躍的冷卻時間。","leveltip":{"label":["傷害","冷卻時間"],"effect":["{{ e1 }} -> {{ e1NL }}","{{ cooldown }} -> {{ cooldownnNL }}"]},"maxrank":5,"cooldown":[20,18,16,14,12],"cooldownBurn":"20/18/16/14/12","cost":[50,50,50,50,50],"costBurn":"50","effect":[null,[65,100,135,170,205],[30,35,40,45,50],[10,10,10,10,10],[2.5,2.5,2.5,2.5,2.5]],"effectBurn":[null,"65/100/135/170/205","30/35/40/45/50","10","2.5"],"vars":[{"link":"bonusattackdamage","coeff":0.2,"key":"a1"}],"costType":"Mana","range":[600,600,600,600,600],"rangeBurn":"600","image":{"full":"KhazixE.png","sprite":"spell4.png","group":"spell","x":336,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48},"altimages":[{"full":"KhazixE0.png","sprite":"spell12.png","group":"spell","x":432,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48}],"resource":"{{ cost }} 魔力"},{"id":"KhazixR","name":"虛空突襲","description":"每一個階段都允許卡力斯進化他其中一項能力，賦予特別的額外效果。當啟動虛空突襲時，卡力斯進入潛行並觸發暗影殺機，同時增加移動速度。如果選擇<span class=\"color00DD33\">進化偽裝</span>，虛空突襲可以施放 3 次，並使卡力斯在潛行時受到的傷害降低。","tooltip":"<span class=\"colorFF9900\">被動：</span>當虛空突襲的等級提升時，卡力斯可以進化其中之一的技能。<br><br><span class=\"colorFF9900\">主動：</span>潛行 {{ e1 }} 秒。啟動暗影殺機可以提高 {{ e3 }}% 跑速，並且在潛行狀態時無視單位碰撞。 虛空突襲可以在 {{ e2 }} 秒內再次施放。<br><br><span class=\"color00DD33\">進化偽裝：</span>可以施放 3 次虛空突襲，並且讓虛空突襲的作用時間延長至 {{ e4 }} 秒。","leveltip":{"label":["進化","冷卻時間"],"effect":["{{ e5 }} -> {{ e5NL }}","{{ cooldown }} -> {{ cooldownnNL }}"]},"maxrank":3,"cooldown":[100,90,80],"cooldownBurn":"100/90/80","cost":[100,100,100],"costBurn":"100","effect":[null,[1,1,1],[15,15,15],[40,40,40],[2,2,2],[1,2,3],[50,50,50]],"effectBurn":[null,"1","15","40","2","1/2/3","50"],"vars":[],"costType":"Mana","range":"self","rangeBurn":"self","image":{"full":"KhazixR.png","sprite":"spell4.png","group":"spell","x":384,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48},"altimages":[{"full":"KhazixR0.png","sprite":"spell12.png","group":"spell","x":0,"y":144,"w":48,"h":48}],"resource":"{{ cost }} 魔力"}],"passive":{"name":"暗影殺機","description":"當卡力斯不在敵方視野時，他會獲得暗影殺機的效果，下一次基礎攻擊造成敵方英雄額外魔法傷害和緩速。","image":{"full":"Khazix_P.png","sprite":"passive1.png","group":"passive","x":96,"y":48,"w":48,"h":48}},"recommended":[{"champion":"Khazix","title":"KhazixDM","type":"riot","map":"8","mode":"ODIN","priority":false,"blocks":[{"type":"starting","items":[{"id":"1001","count":1},{"id":"1036","count":2},{"id":"2003","count":3}]},{"type":"essential","items":[{"id":"3158","count":1},{"id":"3057","count":1},{"id":"3134","count":1}]},{"type":"offensive","items":[{"id":"3078","count":1},{"id":"3071","count":1},{"id":"3181","count":1}]},{"type":"defensive","items":[{"id":"3156","count":1},{"id":"3068","count":1},{"id":"3110","count":1}]},{"type":"Consumables","items":[{"id":"2003","count":1},{"id":"2004","count":1}]}]},{"champion":"Khazix","title":"KhazixTT","type":"riot","map":"10","mode":"CLASSIC","priority":false,"blocks":[{"type":"starting","items":[{"id":"1001","count":1},{"id":"1055","count":1},{"id":"3342","count":1}]},{"type":"essential","items":[{"id":"3158","count":1},{"id":"3057","count":1},{"id":"3134","count":1}]},{"type":"offensive","items":[{"id":"3078","count":1},{"id":"3071","count":1},{"id":"3181","count":1}]},{"type":"defe